    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This namespace contains special index values that represent opacity micro map triangles that have a single transparency state for all sub-triangles. Those values can be used as values in RaytraceGeometryDescription::TrianglesWithOpacityMicroMapInfo::linkage.indexBuffer. Those special index values are preferable over linkages to opacity micro map triangles. </para>
